Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.25,0:01:01.04,Main,Narancia,0,0,0,,D-Do you think the boss is in Venice?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.04,0:01:02.58,Main,Narancia,0,0,0,,Since he mentioned it in the note...
