Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.97,0:01:16.76,Main,Mista,0,0,0,,The station's gonna be dicey, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.76,0:01:20.35,Main,Mista,0,0,0,,Anyone paid off by the enemy \N will rat us out at the drop of a hat.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.89,0:01:24.31,Thoughts,Fugo,0,0,0,,The boss's daughter, Trish...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.11,0:01:28.86,Thoughts,Fugo,0,0,0,,Her life is at risk because of a father she's never met.
